347
00:33:52,764 --> 00:33:54,404
What, what are you doing?

348
00:33:54,933 --> 00:33:57,893
I'll fall, Vl fall
I'm in peril

349
00:33:58,837 --> 00:34:00,327
I'm sweeping the ashes

350
00:34:00,639 --> 00:34:01,539
Won't be a minute

351
00:34:01,773 --> 00:34:03,473
Oh, no
Oh, no

352
00:34:03,808 --> 00:34:05,328
I'm in danger

353
00:34:06,845 --> 00:34:07,895
I'm in danger...

354
00:34:08,446 --> 00:34:09,496
I'll go out

355
00:34:12,684 --> 00:34:15,344
Oh, no
I'm slipping...

356
00:34:21,826 --> 00:34:23,696
Hurry. Sophie

357
00:34:46,150 --> 00:34:48,781
Try not to torment my friend

358
00:34:54,326 --> 00:34:56,406
Master Howl, are you going out?

359
00:34:59,064 --> 00:35:03,104
Markl, tell our cleaning lady
not to get too carried away

360
00:35:08,473 --> 00:35:10,113
What'd you do, Sophie?

361
00:35:11,242 --> 00:35:12,642
She abused me

362
00:35:13,311 --> 00:35:15,801
If I die, Howl goes with me

363
00:35:16,247 --> 00:35:17,557
I'm the cleaning lady

364
00:35:17,849 --> 00:35:19,839
It's my job to clean

365
00:35:21,519 --> 00:35:23,828
No, not the 2nd floor!

366
00:35:24,656 --> 00:35:27,286
If were you, I'd put your
precious things away in a hurry

367
00:35:28,827 --> 00:35:30,467
Save my room for later

368
00:35:33,798 --> 00:35:36,638
My little outburst gave me back
my strength

369
00:35:40,605 --> 00:35:42,625
What a strange house

370
00:36:19,511 --> 00:36:20,851
Amazing!

371
00:36:21,146 --> 00:36:23,136
Calcifer, Calcifer!

372
00:36:23,515 --> 00:36:25,384
Are you moving the castle?

373
00:36:25,750 --> 00:36:27,970
What a lot of fuss! Of course I am

374
00:36:28,386 --> 00:36:29,726
You're incredible, Calcifer

375
00:36:30,355 --> 00:36:33,075
Your magic's first class
I misjudged you completely

376
00:36:36,061 --> 00:36:37,431
You think so?

377
00:36:37,729 --> 00:36:39,538
You really think so!

378
00:36:46,137 --> 00:36:47,947
Oh, no, not yet!

379
00:37:20,605 --> 00:37:21,745
How beautiful

380
