446
00:44:47,018 --> 00:44:48,328
Don't move

447
00:44:48,719 --> 00:44:50,589
They work for the Witch of the Waste

448
00:44:56,761 --> 00:44:57,781
They're gone

449
00:44:58,029 --> 00:45:00,079
Don't people notice
those terrible monsters?

450
00:45:06,170 --> 00:45:07,750
Look! Up there!

451
00:45:08,239 --> 00:45:09,729
That's what dropped those bombs!

452
00:45:10,041 --> 00:45:11,791
An enemy airship, Sophie

453
00:45:17,915 --> 00:45:19,585
Sophie, flyers

454
00:45:20,151 --> 00:45:22,781
lgnore the flyers
They're enemy propaganda!

455
00:45:27,992 --> 00:45:29,392
Are you OK, Sophie?

456
00:45:35,933 --> 00:45:37,483
A glass of water, please

457
00:45:37,802 --> 00:45:38,732
Sure

458
