Sophie, what did you do
to the bathroom shelves? Look!

459
00:45:58,689 --> 00:46:00,359
My hair's turned this weird color!

460
00:46:00,691 --> 00:46:02,330
What... what beautiful hair

461
00:46:02,660 --> 00:46:03,620
Take a good look!

462
00:46:04,228 --> 00:46:06,978
You mixed up everything on
the shelves and ruined the spells

463
00:46:08,666 --> 00:46:10,836
I didn't mix up anything,
I simply cleaned up

464
00:46:11,535 --> 00:46:12,904
Cleaning, always cleaning

465
00:46:13,204 --> 00:46:16,394
