too carried away

466
00:46:16,974 --> 00:46:18,204
It's hopeless

467
00:46:19,377 --> 00:46:21,687
How huniliating

468
00:46:23,714 --> 00:46:25,084
It's not so very bad

469
00:46:33,391 --> 00:46:35,731
This new shade's quite lovely
in its way

470
00:46:36,694 --> 00:46:40,534
I'm done for. What's the point
in living, if you aren't beautiful...

471
00:46:52,843 --> 00:46:55,153
Stop, Howl! Cut it out!

472
00:46:55,980 --> 00:46:57,620
He's calling on
the spirits of Darkness

473
