477
00:47:23,374 --> 00:47:26,004
I've never once been beautiful!

478
00:47:28,145 --> 00:47:29,725
I've had enough of this place!

479
00:48:09,587 --> 00:48:12,627
Thank you, Turnip
You're a kind scarecrow

