Here's some hot milk
Drink up

495
00:49:41,111 --> 00:49:44,451
I'll leave it here
Drink it while it's hot

496
00:49:48,586 --> 00:49:50,196
Don't leave me, Sophie

497
00:49:58,429 --> 00:49:59,889
Try a little milk?

498
