is searching for my house

499
00:50:14,578 --> 00:50:17,618
You're right, 1 saw her cronies
down at the port

500
00:50:18,749 --> 00:50:20,968
The truth is, I'm a coward

501
00:50:21,385 --> 00:50:24,545
All this junk is just sorcery
to keep her away

502
00:50:25,089 --> 00:50:26,578
I'm scared to death

503
00:50:28,459 --> 00:50:31,388
Tell me, why is
the Witch of the Waste after you?

504
00:50:32,563 --> 00:50:36,193
She seemed quite interesting,
so l approached her

505
00:50:36,800 --> 00:50:39,870
But she terrified me
and l ran away

506
00:50:43,340 --> 00:50:46,120
Now the king's ordered
me to report to him

507
00:50:46,610 --> 00:50:48,830
As Jenkins and as Pendragon...

508
00:50:49,246 --> 00:50:51,416
How many names do you use, Howl?

509
00:50:51,815 --> 00:50:53,955
Enough to guarantee my freedom

510
00:50:55,486 --> 00:50:57,566
Can't you refuse the king?

511
00:50:57,955 --> 00:50:59,005
See that...

512
00:50:59,823 --> 00:51:03,393
The oath ! took at
the Sorcery Academy

513
00:51:06,163 --> 00:51:08,443
Say. Howl
Why not visit the king?

514
00:51:09,099 --> 00:51:10,299
What!

515
00:51:11,168 --> 00:51:12,508
Just say it to his face

516
00:51:12,803 --> 00:51:16,173
“Stop this foolish war
lrefuse ta help you"

517
00:51:19,009 --> 00:51:21,199
Sophie, you don't know
what they're like

