only of what's best for his people

519
00:51:27,785 --> 00:51:28,865
l know!

520
00:51:29,219 --> 00:51:31,149
You'll go in my place, Sophie!

521
00:51:33,424 --> 00:51:35,704
Pretend you're Pendragon's mother

522
00:51:36,160 --> 00:51:39,060
Just tell him your son is
an idle good-for-nothing

523
00:51:40,030 --> 00:51:42,170
Maybe Madam Suliman
will even give up on me

524
00:51:42,967 --> 00:51:44,607
Madam Suliman?

525
00:51:48,172 --> 00:51:49,752
You're wearing that hat?

526
00:51:50,174 --> 00:51:52,224
After all the magic 1 spent
making your dress pretty...

