Don't tell me you're Howl

539
00:53:57,434 --> 00:54:01,654
Disguising yourself as an old dog.
of all things

540
00:54:02,339 --> 00:54:04,359
Do you know how exhausting
it is to be old?

541
00:54:07,845 --> 00:54:10,625
How nice to see you
The little hatter, right?

542
00:54:11,381 --> 00:54:12,810
